    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK159">
<l>tuṟantāriṟ tūymai yuṭaiyā riṟantārvā</l>
<l>yiṉṉācco ṉōkkiṟ pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who bear with the uncourteous speech of the insolent are as pure as the ascetics.</l>
            </lg>
